OL,3,CCarol Vorderman quits BBC radio show
OL,4,Cover new social media guidelines
OL,6,FCarol Vorderman will leave her weekly
OL,7,Fshow on BBC Radio Wales after
OL,8,Fbreaking BBC guidelines with vocal
OL,9,Fattacks against the government on
OL,10,Fsocial media
