OL,13,Fleaving her BBC radio show because
OL,14,Fshe is "not prepared to lose my
OL,15,Fvoice" after the corporation
OL,16,Fintroduced new social media
OL,17,Fguidelines.
OL,19,FThe 62-year-old former Countdown star
OL,20,Fhas had a Saturday morning show on
OL,21,FBBC Radio Wales for five years.
